journald-archive (0.2.1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Drop the redundant manual debconf dependency; it is already pulled in via
    ${misc:Depends} as "debconf (>= 0.5) | debconf-2.0".
  * Move the timer helper out of $PATH: install it to
    /usr/lib/journald-archive/ instead of /usr/sbin. It is a private helper
    invoked by the service, not a user command.

 -- Alexander <alexander.s.m@gmail.com>  Sun, 07 Jun 2026 15:01:51 +0000

journald-archive (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add journalctl-all: a wrapper that queries the combined live+archive
    view (/var/log/journal_combined), with bash and zsh completion that
    mirror journalctl's.
  * Ship a journalctl-all(1) manual page.
  * Validate the debconf size answers; re-prompt on non-numeric input
    instead of failing configuration with a cryptic fallocate error.

 -- Alexander <alexander.s.m@gmail.com>  Sun, 07 Jun 2026 14:36:49 +0000

journald-archive (0.1.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Initial release.

